0.1.name: wordpress/snoobi-tracking
0.1.description:
Snoobi Tracking inserts the Snoobi tracking code at the end of every page of your blog. You only have to enter the name your Snoobi account in plugin settings.

Note: your theme should use wp_footer() call. (See footer.php in your theme directory.)
